extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value:
Legendary 5D’s Decks contains THREE complete, ready-to play Decks, each with 50 cards (5 Ultra Rares, 45 Commons per Deck):
A Yusei Deck with 8 brand new cards never released before.
An Akiza Deck designed for use with the new Akiza-themed cards in Doom of Dimensions.
And a Crow Deck featuring the latest Blackwings from 2022’s Darkwing Blast and more!
Each has a 40-card Main Deck and a 10-card Extra Deck (plus a bonus – see below)!
Make no mistake: These Decks contain some of the most popular card tech, from Mulcharmy Meowls to Infinite Impermanence, that can go in whatever Decks you’re playing next. And the 5D’s-themed cards in each Deck aren’t a 1-of-each sampler, but come in the 2’s and 3’s you’ll need to make these Decks really work. It’s time to REV IT UP!
SPECIAL BONUS: Each Deck’s 51st card is a fully-playable chibi art version of that Signer’s main monster (chibi Stardust Dragon for Yusei, chibi Black Rose Dragon for Akiza, and chibi Black-Winged Dragon for Crow)! So you’ll get 3 playable chibi Monster Cards total. You’ll also get 3 different Token Cards, showing chibi art of Yusei, Akiza, and Crow. Going fast makes you feel alive, but looking cute also helps you scoot!
Legendary 5D’s Decks contains:
3 Secret Rare chibi variant art Monster Cards
3 Secret Rare chibi Token Cards
15 Ultra Rares
135 Commons
